---

<Layout title="Maitan Hub | Currículo" sidebarLayout={false}>
  <!-- Sidebar removed -->

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-16 px-6 md:px-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="mb-24" id="resumo">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[60px] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-4 lowercase"
      >
        currículo
      </h1>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <PageNav
          items={[
            { label: "resumo", href: "#resumo" },
            { label: "experiência", href: "#experiencia" },
            { label: "formação", href: "#formacao" },
            { label: "projetos", href: "#projetos" },
            { label: "idiomas", href: "#idiomas" },
          ]}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/LuanMaitan_CV_2025.pdf"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-black dark:text-white border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors lowercase"
        >
          Download PDF
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="14"
            height="14"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"
            ></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line
              x1="12"
              x2="12"
              y1="15"
              y2="3"></line></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://linkedin.com/in/luanmaitan"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-neutral-500 hover:text-black dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors lowercase px-4 py-2"
        >
          Linkedin
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="14"
            height="14"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path
              d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"
            ></path><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect><circle
              cx="4"
              cy="4"
              r="2"></circle></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-24 gap-y-24">
      <!-- Description Section -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
        <p
          class="text-[15px] leading-[1.5] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
        >
          Com formação e especialização nas áreas de letras, linguística e
          editoração, sempre transitei entre grandes produções editoriais e
          científicas, e soluções tecnológicas inovadoras.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-[15px] leading-[1.5] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
        >
          Preparo, reviso e redijo textos há mais de dez anos. Nos últimos,
          assumi cargos de gestão e posições estratégicas, tendo sido
          coordenador editorial, responsável pelo fluxo de edição de algumas das
          maiores revistas científicas do país, e liderado uma área responsável
          pela avaliação de autores para a produção de cursos das mais diversas
          áreas do conhecimento.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-[15px] leading-[1.5] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
        >
          Além disso, gerenciei a garantia da qualidade da produção de conteúdo
          pedagógico multimídia e em soluções de realidade virtual e mista para
          grandes empresas e indústria.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Experiência -->
      <div class="space-y-12 md:col-span-2" id="experiencia">
        <h2
          class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4 mb-8"
        >
          Experiência Profissional
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-16">
          {
            experience.map((job) => (
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-8">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black dark:text-white lowercase tracking-tight">
                    {job.company}
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-10">
                  {job.roles.map((role) => (
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1">
                        <h4 class="text-[16px] font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 lowercase tracking-tight">
                          {role.title}
                        </h4>
                        <span class="text-sm font-mono text-neutral-500 whitespace-nowrap">
                          {role.period}
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.6] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                        {role.description}
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Formação -->
      <div class="space-y-8" id="formacao">
        <h2
          class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
        >
          Formação
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          {
            education.map((edu) => (
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium text-black dark:text-white lowercase">
                  {edu.institution}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[15px] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                  {edu.course}
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-mono text-neutral-500">{edu.period}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Idiomas -->
      <div class="space-y-8" id="idiomas">
        <h2
          class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
        >
          Idiomas
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          {
            languages.map((lang) => (
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
                  <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium text-black dark:text-white lowercase">
                    {lang.name}
                  </h3>
                  <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 px-2 py-0.5 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-full">
                    {lang.level}
                  </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[15px] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                  {lang.description}
                </p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Projetos Pessoais -->
      <div class="space-y-12 md:col-span-2" id="projetos">
        <h2
          class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4 mb-8"
        >
          Projetos Pessoais
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          {
            projects.map((project) => (
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
                  <h3 class="text-[18px] font-medium text-black dark:text-white lowercase">
                    {project.name}
                  </h3>
                  <span class="text-sm font-mono text-neutral-500">
                    {project.period}
                  </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-300 lowercase mb-1">
                  {project.role}
                </p>
                <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.6] text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                  {project.description}
                </p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
